Content:: Abeysinghe Arachchilage Wijethunga (born 16 November 1957) is a Sri Lankan politician. He is a Member of the Parliament of Sri Lanka and former member of the Sabaragamuwa Provincial Council, Ratnapura District UNP Organizer and chief Organizer Kalawana.[1]  This article about a politician from Sabaragamuwa Province, Sri Lanka is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
